snippet.title: Alice's Lullaby Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
!! After years of anticipation, Albino Lullaby, Episode 2: Alice's Lullaby is finally releasing on October 8th on Steam !! 
Embark on a surreal, psychedelic adventure to travel back and forth through time and rescue young Alice, helping her escape the uncanny, macabre and treacherous world of Styx. 
Unravel the metaphysical mystery of the grandchild cult and find out why they call you the monster!
Alice's Lullaby picks up right where Albino Lullaby left off and reveals much more about the mysteries surrounding this nightmare fever dream of a gameworld.
